{"tid":491233,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"面對咁嘅朋友，你會點揀/諗？","createTime":"2017-12-06T10:09:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-06T11:47:15.000Z","uid":138720,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"17104bee7822141793d4ed4f2779a1a9a38038f2","tid":491233,"uid":138720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T10:09:49.000Z","msg":"所謂嘅「兄弟」有事就哎唒大佬<br />\n無事就屌唒你老母<br />\n到你要用錢，又唔想問屋企人攞<br />\n就梗係叫佢地還錢應急<br />\n換嚟嘅只係「無錢啊，下個月先還到」<br />\n同時佢地周圍去，大魚大肉<br />\n最後去到反面階段，佢地先肯還<br />\n仲要打一大堆話金錢顯出人性，顯出朋友嘅價值<br />\n雖然小弟認同喱句講法「講錢失感情」<br />\n但係你地有無諗過，你地要我幫，咁我需要幫嘅時候你地係邊？<br />\n<br />\n各位巴/絲打，你地點睇？"},{"pid":"21c3a67e797df02ffb06a440d5dd9fccbe362026","tid":491233,"uid":76277,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T10:14:50.000Z","msg":"絕交啦唔洗諗"},{"pid":"75919c075d8102b1b518a9a0b38f50d843a9318e","tid":491233,"uid":75754,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T10:15:04.000Z","msg":"真正老死唔會咁"},{"pid":"29ccc1bbc701d5b065537a3ed4f715cbb700c340","tid":491233,"uid":150098,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T10:17:38.000Z","msg":"依種唔係叫朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ddaa79c3e8b672321bef12f2a5bfa6417add393","tid":491233,"uid":161929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T10:32:38.000Z","msg":"借出去要有收唔返既準備<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d6f41fbfb50960a7808d33eb54984e51c095d40","tid":491233,"uid":138720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T10:47:05.000Z","msg":"我仲係full time學生<br />\n佢地就有啲無讀<br />\n同出面同樣無讀嘅人群埋<br />\n其他關唔關價值觀事？"},{"pid":"a80358626e2f9f65f1a30ddfa15e744c12dd3d4a","tid":491233,"uid":138720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T10:47:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我仲係full time學生<br />\n佢地就有啲無讀<br />\n同出面同樣無讀嘅人群埋<br />\n其他關唔關價值觀事？</blockquote><br />\n實"},{"pid":"3e9cd90d9497d45fde294d02073700479fe7d784",